text:
[Verse]
Lights are shining up above
Glowing colors endless love
Dreams are flying with the night
Chasing shadows taking flight

[Verse 2]
Wind is whispering through the trees
Magic moments drifting free
Hearts are beating rhythm true
Underneath the sky so blue

[Chorus]
Into the stars we go oh-oh
Dancing in the cosmic glow oh-oh
Feel the rhythm let it flow oh-oh
Into the stars we go oh-oh

[Verse 3]
Waves are crashing on the shore
Echoes calling
Wanting more
Moon is rising
High and bright
Guiding us through the night

[Bridge]
Hold my hand
Don't let go
In this endless light show
Every step a melody
In our space-bound symphony

[Chorus]
Into the stars we go oh-oh
Dancing in the cosmic glow oh-oh
Feel the rhythm let it flow oh-oh
Into the stars we go oh-oh
title: Into the Stars
